Depends: db4.2-util, univention-ssl, univention-ldap-config, whois, makepasswd, univention-directory-manager-tools | univention-admin-tools, univention-newsid, univention-ipcalc, univention-ldap-acl-master | univention-ldap-acl-slave, bind9-host
Conflicts: univention-5250 (<< 0.5), univention-mail-cyrus-quota-master, univention-admin-nagios (<< 1.0)
Replaces: univention-mail-cyrus-quota-master
Description: UCS - LDAP server configuration
 This package contains the configuration for the OpenLDAP
 server.
 .
